        </div>
        <div id="data">
          <h4> Data and Files </h4>
          <p> We will never log user activity (including clicks, typing, or any other actions on this site, especially on the Contact Form). Any data that goes to us will not be sold (this also applies to website cookies and IP addresses). All data/file(s) that are claimed/owned by you can be removed by contacting <a href="mailto:support@atproducts.xyz">our support line</a>. </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    <div id="acceptance">
      <h3> II: Acceptance</h3>
      <p> By visiting this site, You signify your agreement to the following Privacy Policy.<br> 
        <br> We reserve the right, at our sole discretion, to modify or replace the Privacy Policy at any time. If a revision has a good effect on You, we will make efforts to provide at least a 30-day notice before any new privacy statements take effect. A sufficient revision is determined at our sole discretion.
      </p>
</div>
